      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full probabilistic characterization of all model inputs required including blood rheology parameters.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sampling was applied to geometric tolerances only; blood viscosity and red blood cell fragility distributions were not propagated through the model."
    },
